description: Number of isomorphism classes of connected 3-regular multigraphs of order 2n, loops allowed.
references: A. T. Balaban, Enumeration of Cyclic Graphs, pp. 63-105 of A. T. Balaban, ed., Chemical Applications of Graph Theory, Ac. Press, 1976; see p. 92.
N. J. A. Sloane and Simon Plouffe, The Encyclopedia of Integer Sequences, Academic Press, 1995 (includes this sequence).
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_.
extensions: Using sequence A129427, terms a(12) - a(16) were computed in GAP by Ignat Soroko (ignat.soroko(AT)gmail.com), Apr 07 2010
